items.description_english: When held by a POKéMON, it raises\nthe ATTACK stat in a pinch.
items.description_spanish: Se puede reducir a polvo\npara elaborar una medicina.

items.description_english: When held by a POKéMON, it raises\nthe DEFENSE stat in a pinch.
items.description_spanish: Cuando la lleve un PKMN, le subirá\nel ATAQUE en un momento de apuro.

items.description_english: When held by a POKéMON, it raises\nthe SPEED stat in a pinch.
items.description_spanish: Cuando la lleve un PKMN, le subirá\nla DEFENSA en un momento de apuro.

items.description_english: When held by a POKéMON, it raises\nthe SP. ATK stat in a pinch.
items.description_spanish: Cuando la lleve un PKMN, le subirá\nla VELOC. en un momento de apuro.

items.description_english: When held by a POKéMON, it raises\nthe SP. DEF stat in a pinch.
items.description_spanish: Cuando la lleve un PKMN, le subirá\nel AT.ESP. en un momento de apuro.

items.description_english: When held by a POKéMON, it raises\nthe critical-hit ratio in a pinch.
items.description_spanish: Cuando la lleve un PKMN, le subirá\nla DF.ESP. en un momento de apuro.

items.description_english: When held by a POKéMON, it sharply\nraises one stat in a pinch.
items.description_spanish: Cuando la lleve un PKMN, subirá la\nposibilidad de dar 1 golpe crítico.

items.description_english: Can be ground up into a powder as\nan ingredient for medicine.
items.description_spanish: Cuando la lleve un PKMN, le subirá\n1 caract. en un momento de apuro.
Se puede reducir a polvo\npara elaborar una medicina.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt casts a tricky glare that lowers\nthe opponent's accuracy.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, lanza un destello\nque baja la PRECISIÓN.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt restores any lowered stat in\nbattle. It can be used only once.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, restaura cualquier\ncaracterística debilitada.\nSólo puede usarse una vez.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt promotes strong growth but\nlowers SPEED while it is held.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, se crece con\nfacilidad, pero baja la VELOCIDAD.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nThe holder gets a share of EXP.\npoints without having to battle.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, se toman puntos\nde EXP. de los combates,\nsin que haya que luchar.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA light and sharp claw. The holder\nmay be able to strike first.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, se puede golpear\nen primer lugar.\nEs una garra ligera y veloz.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA bell with a comforting chime that\nmakes the holder calm and friendly.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, calma los ánimos\ny fomenta la amistad.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt snaps the holder out of\ninfatuation. It can be used once.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, los POKéMON\nse liberan del enamoramiento.\nSólo puede usarse una vez.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt powers up one move, which\nbecomes the only usable one.
items.description_spanish: Aumenta la fuerza de un ataque,\npero sólo deja usar ése.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt may cause the foe to flinch\nupon taking damage.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, puede debilitarte\ncuando hieres a tu rival.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA shiny silver powder that boosts\nthe power of BUG-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, se fortalecen\nlos ataques de tipo BICHO.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt doubles the battle money if the\nholding POKéMON takes part.
items.description_spanish: Si el que lo lleva lucha en un\ncombate, duplica el dinero.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt repels wild POKéMON if the\nholder is first in the party.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo el primero del equipo,\nlos POKéMON salvajes no se\nacercan.

items.description_english: An orb to be held by a LATIOS or\nLATIAS. It raises the SP. ATK\nand SP. DEF stats.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, suben el AT. ESP. y\nla DEF. ESP. de LATIOS y LATIAS.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA fang that gleams a sharp silver.\nIt raises the SP. ATK stat.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, sube el AT. ESP.\nde CLAMPERL.\nBrilla como la plata.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA scale that shines a faint pink.\nIt raises the SP. DEF stat.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, sube la DEF. ESP.\nde CLAMPERL.\nTiene un brillo rosado.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nThe holding POKéMON can flee from\nany wild POKéMON for sure.
items.description_spanish: Se usa para huir de combates\ncontra POKéMON salvajes.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nThe holding POKéMON is prevented\nfrom evolving.
items.description_spanish: El POKéMON que lleve esta piedra\nmágica no evolucionará.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nThe holding POKéMON may endure an\nattack, leaving just 1 HP.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, quizá evites\ndebilitarte. Puede que al menos\nte quedes con 1 PS.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nAn egg filled with happiness that\nearns extra EXP. points in battle.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, ganarás muchos más\npuntos de EXP. en combate.\nEstá lleno de felicidad.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA lens that boosts the critical-hit\nratio of the holding POKéMON.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, la lente aumenta\nla posibilidad de golpe crítico.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA special metallic film that boosts\nthe power of STEEL-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, la película metálica\nfortalece los ataques de tipo\nACERO.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nThe holding POKéMON gradually\nregains HP during battle.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlos, van restaurando\nlos PS durante el combate.

items.description_english: A thick and tough scale.\nA DRAGON-type POKéMON may be\nholding it.
items.description_spanish: Peculiar y sólida escama que\npueden llevar los POKéMON\nde tipo DRAGÓN.

items.description_english: An orb to be held by a PIKACHU\nthat raises the SP. ATK stat.\nTouching it may cause a shock.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, el AT. ESP. \nde PIKACHU aumentará.\nPuede dar calambre.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA loose, silky sand that boosts the\npower of GROUND-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, la suavidad de la\narena fortalece los ataques\nde tipo TIERRA.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nAn unbreakable stone that boosts\nthe power of ROCK-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, la robustez de la\npiedra fortalece los ataques\nde tipo ROCA.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA seed imbued with life that boosts\nthe power of GRASS-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, la vitalidad de la\nsemilla fortalece los ataques\nde tipo PLANTA.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA shady-looking pair of glasses\nthat boosts DARK-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlas, se fortalecen\nlos ataques de tipo SINIESTRO.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA belt that boosts determination\nand FIGHTING-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, aumenta la decisión\ny se fortalecen los ataques\nde tipo LUCHA.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA powerful magnet that boosts the\npower of ELECTRIC-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, el fuerte magnetismo\nfortalece los ataques de tipo\nELÉCTRICO.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA teardrop-shaped gem that boosts\nthe power of WATER-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, la forma de lágrima de\nla gema hace que se fortalezcan\nlos ataques de tipo AGUA.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA long, sharp beak that boosts the\npower of FLYING-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, se fortalecen\nlos ataques de tipo VOLADOR.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA small, poisonous barb that boosts\nthe power of POISON-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, el contenido tóxico\nfortalece los ataques de tipo\nVENENO.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA piece of ice that repels heat\nand boosts ICE-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, la frialdad del trozo\nde hielo hace que se fortalezcan\nlos ataques de tipo HIELO.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA sinister, eerie tag that boosts\nGHOST-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, aumenta la energía\noscura y se fortalecen\nlos ataques de tipo FANTASMA.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA spoon imbued with telekinetic\npower boosts PSYCHIC-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla, la energía telequiné-\ntica de la cuchara fortalece\nlos ataques de tipo PSÍQUICO.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA combustible fuel that boosts the\npower of FIRE-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, actúa como combustible\ny fortalece los ataques de tipo\nFUEGO.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA hard and sharp fang that boosts\nthe power of DRAGON-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, la dureza del colmillo\nfortalece los ataques de tipo\nDRAGÓN.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nA sumptuous scarf that boosts the\npower of NORMAL-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, la delicadeza del\npañuelo fortalece los ataques\nde tipo NORMAL.

items.description_english: A transparent device filled with all\nsorts of data.\nIt is made by SILPH CO.
items.description_spanish: Peculiar caja hecha en SILPH S.A.\nEstá llena de cosas.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nThe holding POKéMON regains some\nHP upon striking the foe.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarla y vencer al enemigo,\nrestaura los PS.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt slightly boosts the power of\nWATER-type moves.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, los ataques tipo AGUA\nson algo más fuertes.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIts tricky aroma slightly reduces\nthe foe's accuracy.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, gracias al aroma\nque libera, baja algo la\nPRECISIÓN del rival.

items.description_english: A glove to be held by a CHANSEY.\nIt raises CHANSEY's critical-hit\nratio.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo, CHANSEY dará\nposiblemente un golpe crítico.

items.description_english: A fine, hard powder to be held by\na DITTO.\nIt raises DITTO's DEFENSE stat.
items.description_spanish: Si lo lleva DITTO, gracias a la\ndureza del polvo, aumentará\nsu DEFENSA.

items.description_english: A hard bone of some sort to be\nheld by a CUBONE or MAROWAK.\nIt raises the ATTACK stat.
items.description_spanish: Extraño tipo de hueso. Suelen\nllevarlo CUBONE o MAROWAK.\nAumenta el ATAQUE.

items.description_english: A stick of leek to be held by a\nFARFETCH'D. It raises FARFETCH'D's\ncritical-hit ratio.
items.description_spanish: Es un puerro. Suele llevarlo\nFARFETCH'D. Le facilita dar\nun golpe crítico.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt boosts the holding POKéMON's\nCOOL condition in CONTESTS.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo en los CONCURSOS\naumenta el CARISMA.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt boosts the holding POKéMON's\nBEAUTY condition in CONTESTS.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo en los CONCURSOS\naumenta la BELLEZA.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt boosts the holding POKéMON's\nCUTE condition in CONTESTS.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo en los CONCURSOS\naumenta la DULZURA.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt boosts the holding POKéMON's\nSMART condition in CONTESTS.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo en los CONCURSOS\naumenta el INGENIO.

items.description_english: An item to be held by a POKéMON.\nIt boosts the holding POKéMON's\nTOUGH condition in CONTESTS.
items.description_spanish: Al llevarlo en los CONCURSOS\naumenta la DUREZA.

items.description_english: A folding bicycle that is at least\ntwice as fast as walking.
items.description_spanish: Bici plegable con la que se va\nel doble de rápido que a pie.

items.description_english: A case for holding COINS obtained\nat the GAME CORNER.\nIt holds up to 9,999 COINS.
items.description_spanish: Te servirá para llevar hasta 9.999\nmonedas. Se obtiene en el CASINO.

items.description_english: A device used for finding items.\nIf there is a hidden item nearby\nwhen it is used, it emits a signal.
items.description_spanish: Detector de objetos invisibles\npor ondas sonoras. Emite una señal\ncuando encuentra un objeto.

items.description_english: An old and beat-up fishing rod.\nUse it by any body of water to \nfish for wild POKéMON.
items.description_spanish: Pesca POKéMON salvajes en todo\ntipo de aguas.\nNo está nada nueva.

items.description_english: A new, good-quality fishing rod.\nUse it by any body of water to \nfish for wild POKéMON.
items.description_spanish: Una buena caña para pescar\nPOKéMON salvajes.\nEs de muy buena calidad.

items.description_english: An awesome, high-tech fishing rod.\nUse it by any body of water to fish\nfor wild POKéMON.
items.description_spanish: Es la mejor caña para pescar\nPOKéMON salvajes.\nEs de alta tecnología.

items.description_english: The ticket required for sailing on\nthe ferry S.S. ANNE.\nIt has a drawing of a ship on it.
items.description_spanish: Es el billete válido para embarcar\nen el S.S. ANNE.\nTiene dibujado un barco.

items.description_english: The pass required for entering\nPOKéMON CONTESTS. It has a\ndrawing of an award ribbon on it.
items.description_spanish: Es necesario para participar\nen un CONCURSO POKéMON.\nTiene dibujada una cinta.

items.description_english: A nifty watering pail.\nUse it to promote strong growth in\nBERRIES planted in soft soil.
items.description_spanish: Sirve para regar las BAYAS\ny las plantas.

items.description_english: A package that contains mechanical\nparts of some sort made by the\nDEVON CORPORATION.
items.description_spanish: Paquete con todas las piezas\nde la máquina de DEVON S.A.

items.description_english: A sack used to collect volcanic\nash automatically during walks\nover deep ash.
items.description_spanish: Saco usado para recoger y\nguardar cenizas volcánicas\nal caminar.

items.description_english: The key to NEW MAUVILLE, which\nwas constructed beneath MAUVILLE\nCITY.
items.description_spanish: Llave de MALVALANOVA (al sur\nde CIUDAD MALVALONA).

items.description_english: A folding bicycle that is capable\nof stunts like jumps and wheelies.
items.description_spanish: Bici plegable ideal para saltar\ny hacer caballitos y giros.

items.description_english: A case for holding {POKEBLOCK}S made\nwith a BERRY BLENDER. It releases\none {POKEBLOCK} when shaken.
items.description_spanish: Tubo para los {POKEBLOCK}S\nhechos con la LICUABAYAS.\nAgitar antes de usar.

items.description_english: An extremely important letter to\nSTEVEN from the PRESIDENT of the\nDEVON CORPORATION.
items.description_spanish: Importante carta para MÁXIMO,\ndel PRESIDENTE de DEVON S.A.

items.description_english: The ticket required for sailing on a\nferry to a distant southern island.\nIt features a drawing of an island.
items.description_spanish: El billete necesario para ir\nhasta una lejana isla del sur.\nTiene dibujada una isla.

items.description_english: An orb that glows red.\nIt is said to contain an incredible\npower from ancient times.
items.description_spanish: Es roja y brillante. Dicen que\nposee un poder ancestral.

items.description_english: An orb that glows blue.\nIt is said to contain an incredible\npower from ancient times.
items.description_spanish: Es azul y brillante. Dicen que\nposee un poder ancestral.

items.description_english: A device used to search for\nlife-forms in water.\nIt looks too difficult to use.
items.description_spanish: Dispositivo encontrado\nen la NAO ABANDONADA.\nParece difícil de usar.

items.description_english: A pair of protective goggles.\nThey enable a TRAINER to travel\nthrough even desert sandstorms.
items.description_spanish: Ingeniosas gafas que protegen\nde la arena del desierto.

items.description_english: A meteorite that fell from space\nonto MT. MOON long ago.\nIt is very lumpy and hard.
items.description_spanish: Meteorito encontrado\nen la CASCADA METEORO.\nEs poroso y duro.

items.description_english: A key that opens the door to Room\n1 inside the ABANDONED SHIP.\nIt is old and looks easily broken.
items.description_spanish: Llave de la CABINA 1\nde la NAO ABANDONADA.\nEstá vieja y se ve frágil.

items.description_english: A key that opens the door to Room\n2 inside the ABANDONED SHIP.\nIt is old and looks easily broken.
items.description_spanish: Llave de la CABINA 2\nde la NAO ABANDONADA.\nEstá vieja y se ve frágil.

items.description_english: A key that opens the door to Room\n4 inside the ABANDONED SHIP.\nIt is old and looks easily broken.
items.description_spanish: Llave de la CABINA 4\nde la NAO ABANDONADA.\nEstá vieja y se ve frágil.

items.description_english: A key that opens the door to Room\n6 inside the ABANDONED SHIP.\nIt is old and looks easily broken.
items.description_spanish: Llave de la CABINA 6\nde la NAO ABANDONADA.\nEstá vieja y se ve frágil.

items.description_english: A key that opens the storage hold\ninside the ABANDONED SHIP.\nIt is old and looks easily broken.
items.description_spanish: Llave del ALMACÉN de la NAO\nABANDONADA.\nEstá vieja y se ve frágil.

items.description_english: A fossil of an ancient, seafloor-\ndwelling POKéMON. It appears to be\npart of a plant root.
items.description_spanish: Fósil de un POKéMON ancestral\nque vivía en el fondo del mar.\nParece ser parte de una raíz.

items.description_english: A fossil of an ancient, seafloor-\ndwelling POKéMON. It appears to be\npart of a claw.
items.description_spanish: Fósil de un POKéMON ancestral\nque vivía en el fondo del mar.\nParece ser parte de una garra.

items.description_english: A scope that signals the presence\nof any unseeable POKéMON.\nIt is made by the DEVON CORP.
items.description_spanish: Dispositivo hecho en DEVON\npara ver POKéMON invisibles.

items.description_english:
An attack that is
executed last.
The user flinches
if hit beforehand.
items.description_spanish:
Es tardío, pero
si el rival
te golpea
no te moverás.

items.description_english:
Sharp, huge claws
hook and slash the
foe quickly and
with great power.
items.description_spanish: Araña al rival\ncon garras\nafiladas.

items.description_english:
An attack with a
pulsing blast of
water. It may also
confuse the foe.
items.description_spanish: Ondas ultrasónicas\nque pueden\nconfundir al rival.

items.description_english:
The user focuses
its mind to raise
the SP. ATK and
SP. DEF stats.
items.description_spanish: Sube el AT. ESP.\ny la DEF. ESP.\ncon concentración.

items.description_english:
The foe is made to
switch out with an
ally. In the wild,
the battle ends.
items.description_spanish:
Ahuyenta al rival
y finaliza el
combate.Ahuyenta al rival
y finaliza el
combate.

items.description_english:
A move that badly
poisons the foe.
Its poison damage
worsens every turn.
items.description_spanish: Envenena al rival\nde forma\nprogresiva.

items.description_english: Tormenta de granizo\nque golpea en cada\nturno.
items.description_spanish:
A hailstorm lasting
five turns damages
all POKéMON except
the ICE-type.

items.description_english:
The user bulks up
its body to boost
both its ATTACK and
DEFENSE stats.
items.description_spanish:
Robustece el
cuerpo para
subir ATAQUE
y DEFENSA.

items.description_english:
The user shoots
seeds at the foe.
Two to five seeds
are shot at once.
items.description_spanish: Dispara de 2 a 5\nráfagas consecu-\ntivas de semillas.

items.description_english:
An attack that
varies in type and
intensity depending
on the user.
items.description_spanish: Su eficacia varía\nsegún el agresor.

items.description_english:
The sun blazes for
five turns, powering
up FIRE-type
moves.
items.description_spanish: Sube los ataques\nde tipo FUEGO\ndurante 5 turnos.

items.description_english:
The foe is taunted
into a rage that
allows it to use
only attack moves.
items.description_spanish: Hace que el rival\nsólo use ataques.

items.description_english:
The foe is struck
with an icy beam.
It may freeze the
foe solid.
items.description_spanish: Rayo de hielo\nque puede llegar\na congelar.

items.description_english:
The foe is blasted
with a blizzard.
It may freeze the
foe solid.
items.description_spanish: Tormenta de hielo\nque puede llegar\na congelar.

items.description_english:
A severely damaging
attack that makes
the user rest on
the next turn.
items.description_spanish: Es eficaz, pero\ndeja inmóvil al\natacante 1 turno.

items.description_english:
A wall of light
cuts damage from
SP. ATK attacks
for five turns.
items.description_spanish: Reduce el daño que\ncausa el AT. ESP.\ndel rival.

items.description_english:
Enables the user to
evade all attacks.
It may fail if used
in succession.
items.description_spanish: Frena ataques,\npero puede fallar\nsi se usa sin cesar.

items.description_english:
A heavy rain falls
for five turns,
powering up WATER-
type moves.
items.description_spanish:
Refuerza los
ataques de
tipo AGUA
durante 5 turnos.

items.description_english:
A harsh attack that
absorbs half the
damage it inflicted
to restore HP.
items.description_spanish: Absorbe la\nmitad del daño\nproducido.

items.description_english:
It protects the
user's party from
all status problems
for five turns.
items.description_spanish:
Fuerza mística
que evita
problemas
de estado.

items.description_english: Es más fuerte si\nno se aprecia\nal ENTRENADOR.
items.description_spanish:
This attack move
grows more powerful
the less the user
likes its TRAINER.

items.description_english:
A 2-turn move that
blasts the foe with
absorbed energy in
the 2nd turn.
items.description_spanish: 1.{SUPER_ER} turno: absorbe\nluz.\n2.: ataca.

items.description_english:
An attack with a
steel-hard tail.
It may lower the
foe's DEFENSE stat.
items.description_spanish:
Ataca con una
cola férrea
y puede bajar
la DEFENSA.

items.description_english:
A strong electrical
attack that may
also leave the foe
paralyzed.
items.description_spanish:
Duro ataque
eléctrico que
puede paralizar
al enemigo.

items.description_english:
A brutal lightning
attack that may
also leave the foe
paralyzed.
items.description_spanish: Un estruendo que\npuede paralizar\nal enemigo.

items.description_english:
An earthquake that
strikes all POKéMON
in battle excluding
the user.
items.description_spanish: Fuerte, pero inútil\ncontra voladores.

items.description_english:
This attack move
grows more powerful
the more the user
likes its TRAINER.
items.description_spanish: Ataque que aumenta\nsus efectos con\nla amistad.

items.description_english:
An attack that hits
on the 2nd turn.
Can also be used
to exit dungeons.
items.description_spanish: 1.{SUPER_ER} turno: cava.\n2.: ataca.

items.description_english:
A strong telekinetic
attack. It may also
lower the foe's
SP. DEF stat.
items.description_spanish:
Fuerte ataque
psíquico que
puede bajar
la DEF. ESP.

items.description_english:
A shadowy blob is
hurled at the foe.
May also lower the
foe's SP. DEF.
items.description_spanish: Lanza una bola\nnegra que puede\nbajar la DEF. ESP.

items.description_english:
An attack that also
breaks any barrier
like LIGHT SCREEN
and REFLECT.
items.description_spanish: Destruye barreras\ncomo REFLEJO\ny causa daño.

items.description_english:
The user creates
illusory copies of
itself to raise its
evasiveness.
items.description_spanish: Crea espejismos\npara mejorar\nla EVASIÓN.

items.description_english:
A wall of light
cuts damage from
physical attacks
for five turns.
items.description_spanish: Pared de luz\nque debilita los\nataques físicos.

items.description_english:
A rapid jolt of
electricity strikes
the foe. It can't
be evaded.
items.description_spanish: Ataque eléctrico\nmuy rápido\ne ineludible.

items.description_english:
The foe is scorched
with intense flames.
The foe may suffer
a burn.
items.description_spanish: Fuerte ataque que\npuede causar\nquemaduras.

items.description_english:
Filthy sludge is
hurled at the foe.
It may poison the
target.
items.description_spanish: Explosión de lodo\nque puede llegar\na envenenar.

items.description_english:
A 5-turn sandstorm
that damages all
types except ROCK,
GROUND, and STEEL.
items.description_spanish: Tormenta de arena\nque dura varios\nturnos.

items.description_english:
The foe is hit with
an intense flame.
It may leave the
target with a burn.
items.description_spanish:
Llama que lo
chamusca todo
y suele causar
quemadura.

items.description_english:
Boulders are hurled
at the foe. It also
lowers the foe's
SPEED if it hits.
items.description_spanish:
Tira rocas al
rival, lo para
y suele bajarle
VELOCIDAD.

items.description_english:
An extremely fast
attack against one
target. It can't be
evaded.
items.description_spanish: Ataque tremenda-\nmente rápido\ne ineludible.

items.description_english:
It enrages the foe,
making it incapable
of using the same
move successively.
items.description_spanish: Agobia e impide\nel uso reiterado\nde un ataque.

items.description_english:
An attack that is
boosted if user is
burned, poisoned,
or paralyzed.
items.description_spanish:
Potencia el ATAQUE
al estar quemado,
paralizado o
envenenado.

items.description_english:
An attack that may
have an additional
effect that varies
with the terrain.
items.description_spanish: Los efectos de este\nataque varían\nsegún la zona.

items.description_english:
The user sleeps for
two turns to fully
restore HP and heal
any status problem.
items.description_spanish: Te duerme durante\n2 turnos para\ncurarte totalmente.

items.description_english:
If it is the other
gender, the foe is
made infatuated and
unlikely to attack.
items.description_spanish: Reduce la\nposibilidad de que\nel enemigo ataque.

items.description_english:
n attack that may
take the foe's held
item if the user
isn't holding one.
items.description_spanish: Puede quitarle\nal rival el objeto\nque lleve.

items.description_english:
The foe is hit with
wings of steel.
It may also raise
the user's DEFENSE.
items.description_spanish: Alas rígidas que\ngolpean al rival.

items.description_english:
The user employs
its psychic power
to swap abilities
with the foe.
items.description_spanish: Intercambia la\nhabilidad especial\ncon otro POKéMON.

items.description_english:
Steals the effects
of the foe's
healing or status-
changing move.
items.description_spanish:
Roba el efecto
del ataque
que el rival
use después.

items.description_english:
An intense attack
that also sharply
reduces the user's
SP. ATK stat.
items.description_spanish:
Ataque en toda
regla que
baja mucho
tu AT. ESP.

items.description_english:
A basic attack.
It can be used to
cut down thin trees
and grass.
items.description_spanish:
Corta con garras,
guadañas, etc.
Fuera de combate
se usa para cortar.

items.description_english:
A 2-turn move that
hits on the 2nd
turn. Use it to fly
to any known town.
items.description_spanish:
1.{SUPER_ER} turno: vuela.
2.: ataca. Fuera
de combate lleva a
sitios conocidos.

items.description_english:
A big wave crashes
down on the foe.
Can also be used
for crossing water.
items.description_spanish:
Lanza una gran ola
al rival.
Fuera de combate
sirve para nadar.

items.description_english:
The foe is slugged
at maximum power.
Can also be used
to move boulders.
items.description_spanish:
Potente ataque
físico. Fuera de
combate sirve para
mover piedras.

items.description_english:
A blast of light
that cuts the foe's
accuracy. It also
illuminates caves.
items.description_spanish:
Luz cegadora que
baja la PRECISIÓN.
Fuera de combate
sirve para iluminar.

items.description_english:
An attack that may
also cut DEFENSE.
It can also smash
cracked boulders.
items.description_spanish:
Ataque que puede
bajar la DEFENSA.
Fuera de combate
machaca rocas.

items.description_english:
A powerful charge
attack. It can also
be used to climb
a waterfall.
items.description_spanish:
Embiste con impulso
para remontar
una cascada incluso
fuera de combate.

items.description_english:
The user dives
underwater on the
first turn and
strikes next turn.
items.description_spanish: 1.{SUPER_ER} turno: bucea.\n2.: golpea.

items.description_english: A parcel to be delivered to PROF.\nOAK from VIRIDIAN CITY's POKéMON\nMART.
items.description_spanish: Correo que hay que entregar al\nPROF. OAK. Se lo envían desde la\nTIENDA POKéMON de CIUDAD VERDE.

items.description_english: A flute that is said to instantly\nawaken any POKéMON. It has a\nlovely tone.
items.description_spanish: Dicen que consigue despertar al\ninstante a cualquier POKéMON.\nSuena de maravilla.

items.description_english: The key to CINNABAR ISLAND GYM's\nfront door. It is colored red and\ndecorated.
items.description_spanish: Es la llave de la puerta principal\ndel GIMNASIO de ISLA CANELA.\nEs roja y está decorada.

items.description_english: Take this voucher to the BIKE SHOP\nin CERULEAN CITY and exchange it\nfor a bicycle.
items.description_spanish: Puede canjearse por una bici en\nla TIENDA de BICIS de CIUDAD\nCELESTE.

items.description_english: A set of false teeth lost by the\nSAFARI ZONE'S WARDEN. It makes his\nsmile sparkle.
items.description_spanish: Son los dientes de oro que perdió\nel GUARDA del SAFARI. Con ellos,\ntenía una sonrisa de anuncio.

items.description_english: A piece of amber that contains\nthe genes of an ancient POKéMON.\nIt is clear with a reddish tint.
items.description_spanish: Trozo de ámbar que contiene \ninformación genética de un POKéMON\nancestral. Es cristalino y rojizo.

items.description_english: A card-type key that unlocks doors\nin SILPH CO.'s HEAD OFFICE in\nSAFFRON CITY.
items.description_spanish: Tarjeta magnética que abre las\npuertas de las OFICINAS CENTRALES\nde SILPH S.A. en CIUDAD AZAFRÁN.

items.description_english: A key that operates the elevator\nin TEAM ROCKET's HIDEOUT.\nIt bears the TEAM ROCKET logo.
items.description_spanish: LLave del ascensor de la GUARIDA\ndel TEAM ROCKET.\nTiene el símbolo de la banda.

items.description_english: A fossil of an ancient, seafloor-\ndwelling POKéMON. It appears to be\npart of a seashell.
items.description_spanish: Fósil de un POKéMON ancestral que\nvivió en el fondo del mar. Parece\nser un trozo de una concha marina.

items.description_english: A fossil of an ancient, seafloor-\ndwelling POKéMON. It appears to be\npart of a shell.
items.description_spanish: Fósil de un POKéMON ancestral\nque vivió en el fondo del mar.\nParece ser un trozo de una concha.

items.description_english: A scope that makes unseeable\nPOKéMON visible.\nIt is made by SILPH CO.
items.description_spanish: Dispositivo hecho en SILPH S.A.\npara ver POKéMON invisibles.

items.description_english: A folding bicycle that allows\nfaster movement than the RUNNING\nSHOES.
items.description_spanish: Bici plegable con la que se va más\nrápido que con las DEPORTIVAS.

items.description_english: A very convenient map that can be\nviewed anytime. It even shows your \npresent location.
items.description_spanish: Útil mapa que puede consultarse\nen cualquier momento.\nTambién indica dónde te encuentras.

items.description_english: A device that indicates TRAINERS\nwho want to battle. The battery\ncharges while traveling.
items.description_spanish: Dispositivo que busca a los\nENTRENADORES que quieren luchar.\nLa batería se carga al caminar.

items.description_english: A device that enables you to\nrecall what you've heard and seen\nabout famous people.
items.description_spanish: Dispositivo que da información\nsobre cosas y personas con las\nque te has encontrado.

items.description_english: A case that holds TMs and HMs.\nIt is attached to the BAG's\ncompartment for important items.
items.description_spanish: Tubo que contiene las MT y MO.\nEstá en el bolsillo de los objetos\nclave de la MOCHILA.

items.description_english: A pouch for carrying BERRIES.\nIt is attached to the BAG's\ncompartment for important items.
items.description_spanish: Saquito que sirve para llevar las\nBAYAS. Está en el bolsillo de los\nobjetos clave de la MOCHILA.

items.description_english: A television set that is tuned to\na program with useful tips for\nnovice TRAINERS.
items.description_spanish: Tele de bolsillo que emite consejos\nmuy útiles para ENTRENADORES\nnovatos.

items.description_english: A pass for ferries between ONE,\nTWO, and THREE ISLAND.\nIt has a drawing of three islands.
items.description_spanish: Ticket necesario para usar el ferry\nque une ISLA PRIMA, SECUNDA y\nTERA. Tiene el dibujo de las tres.

items.description_english: A pass for ferries between\nVERMILION and the SEVII ISLANDS.\nIt features a drawing of a rainbow.
items.description_spanish: Ticket necesario para usar el ferry\nque une CARMÍN y ARCHI7. Tiene\ndibujado un arco iris.

items.description_english: An aromatic tea prepared by an old\nlady. It will slake even the worst\nthirst.
items.description_spanish: Té de hierbas aromáticas preparado\npor una señora mayor. Apaga la sed\na cualquiera.

items.description_english: A ticket required to board the ship\nto NAVEL ROCK.\nIt glows with a mystic light.
items.description_spanish: Ticket necesario para navegar\nhasta ROCA OMBLIGO.\nBrilla de una forma misteriosa.

items.description_english: A ticket required to board the ship\nto BIRTH ISLAND.\nIt glows beautifully.
items.description_spanish: Ticket necesario para navegar\nhasta ISLA ORIGEN.\nTiene un brillo precioso.

items.description_english: A jar for storing BERRY POWDER\nmade using a BERRY CRUSHER.
items.description_spanish: Bote que sirve para guardar el\nPOLVO de BAYA que se obtiene\ncon el MACHACABAYAS.

items.description_english: An exquisitely beautiful gem that\nhas a red glow.\nIt symbolizes passion.
items.description_spanish: Gema de extraordinaria belleza\ny brillo rojizo.\nSimboliza el entusiasmo.

items.description_english: An exquisitely beautiful gem that\nhas a blue glow.\nIt symbolizes honesty.
items.description_spanish: Gema de extraordinaria belleza\ny brillo azulado.\nSimboliza la sinceridad.
